Papɩzʋʋ posusi tɔm ndʋ kɛ, efemiye kʋɖʋmɖɩyɛ yaa afema sakɩyɛ cabɩ pazɩ. Tɔm kuzusutu wɛna wazaɣ siŋŋ kɛ samaɣ hɛkʋ taa. Pɩcɔ nɛ samaɣ yaa ɛyaa sakɩyɛ nɩ-ɩ tɔm ndɩ ndɩ lɛ, pʋwɛna tɔm ndʋ tɩtɩnaɣ size posusi tʋ. Tɔm kususutu ndʋ, tɩwɛ fevere mbʋ pɩ-yɔɔ yɔ, tɩ-talɩʋ paa le.

